  [0m[2m[38;5;240m│[0m   Great terminal interfaces do not imitate the web; they borrow its clarity.                 [0m[2m[38;5;240m│[0m  
  [0m[2m[38;5;240m│[0m   Spacing, focus, and motion matter even more when every pixel is a character.               [0m[2m[38;5;240m│[0m  
  [0m[2m[38;5;240m│[0m   Silvery helps you compose views that feel calm under pressure, whether you are             [0m[2m[38;5;240m│[0m  
